data.description: The Prized Pamlico. Step inside the most modern and desired floor plan from builder Four Season in one of the newest homes Nash County has to offer! Move in-ready and recently constructed in 2023, the sellers wouldn't leave it if they didn't have to! This home features every modern amenity a home owner seeks such as LVP flooring, granite counters, Kitchen Island, pantry, stainless appliances,  permanently affixed stairs leading to the floored attic that allows for living space expansion, and so much more. 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms include a primary suite with attached lux private bathroom. Large covered front porch overlooks the nearly 1 acre cleared lot. Experience new construction convenience without the hassle of waiting and going through the tedious process of a build. Come see this like-new home for yourself and you'll see exactly what I'm talking about!
